title: $:/plugins/rimir/kind/changelog
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|v0.1.64 |2026-06-04 |Graph tooltip node actions + modal: hover tooltip on every kind-graph node (Instances Overview + Context preview) gains ''edit'' (live field editor in a modal), ''delete'' (confirm dialog; disabled with a hint while the node has `parent`-field children — guard re-checked in the modal) and ''Add child'' buttons for every kind whose `parent` ref field accepts the node's type (plus `kind.parent-kinds` children, `kg.child-kinds`). Create reuses the standard editor + `kind.finalize-create` with parent pre-filled and defaults applied. New `$:/plugins/rimir/kind/graph-modal` overlay (`$:/tags/AboveStory`, layered above the cascade-palette); tooltip buttons dismiss the graph popup on click. |
|v0.1.63 |2026-06-03 |Cascade-palette "Kind icons" structure toggle — when on, every menu row backed by a kind instance shows its type's `kind.icon` glyph at the front (all views, persists across reloads). Off by default; appears only while a kind type exists. Needs cascade-palette ≥0.0.109. |
|v0.1.62 |2026-06-02 |Refactor: `kind.kv` JSON-pair helper + `kind.finalize-create` save-flow consolidation. |
|v0.1.61 |2026-06-02 |Context preview: graph fills the side-preview pane's visible height (no scrolling). |
|v0.1.60 |2026-06-02 |Perf: graph edge colour/stroke computed per-field once, not per-edge. |
|v0.1.59 |2026-06-02 |Context preview: edge + type pills, colour-coded edges; graph + stylesheet fixes. |
|v0.1.58 |2026-06-02 |New: //Context// cascade-palette side-preview + shared graph module. |
|v0.1.57 |2026-06-02 |New: //Kind: Instances Overview// graph view. |
|v0.1.56 |2026-06-01 |Fix: dependent-default cascade didn't re-fire on ref/enum pick in either creator OR cascade-palette. |
|v0.1.55 |2026-05-31 |Unified `default` as a subfilter — dynamic defaults that read from the draft, re-fire after ref/enum changes. |
|v0.1.54 |2026-05-31 |Cascade-palette: structured CRUD drill for `kind.auto-children` — no more JSON typing. |
|v0.1.53 |2026-05-31 |Surface child kinds on the parent's editing UI + type-safe parent-kinds picker in CP + auto-create child instances on parent save. |
|v0.1.52 |2026-05-31 |Add child kinds + cascade-palette //Create here…// action. |
|v0.1.51 |2026-05-29 |Fix: ref field with no `ref-types` now lists all kind-instances instead of every tiddler in the wiki. |
|v0.1.50 |2026-05-28 |Bridge to cascade-palette ≥ 0.0.79: catalogue actions surface in every view automatically. |
|v0.1.49 |2026-05-28 |Migrate instance-view preview to cascade-palette's new tag-based side-preview protocol. |
|v0.1.48 |2026-05-28 |Move kind-instance view from Ctrl-hold detail drawer into the side-preview pane + live preview for create/edit + card-style redesign. |
|v0.1.47 |2026-05-28 |Four create-flow UX fixes — Reset row, Ctrl-Enter mass-create, draft re-seeding, DEL-to-unset field. |
|v0.1.46 |2026-05-27 |Perf: unique-constraint walks no longer scan every tiddler in the wiki on every render. |
|v0.1.45 |2026-05-27 |Fix: constraint violations no longer let users save invalid entities. |
|v0.1.44 |2026-05-27 |Big round: per-field `default` property with token expansion, multi-cardinality text fields, several latent bugs fixed. |
|v0.1.43 |2026-05-27 |Fix: delete-kind dialog always said //no instances exist// — instance count was broken since 0.1.39. |
|v0.1.42 |2026-05-27 |Fix: Save and Warning rows showed icon twice (💾💾 / ⛔⛔). |
|v0.1.41 |2026-05-27 |Save row previews computed title in its ca-name: `💾 Save as "<title>"`. |
|v0.1.40 |2026-05-27 |Disable Save when title-formula yields empty — show diagnostic warning row instead. |
|v0.1.39 |2026-05-27 |DEL-key delete on kind rows in Manage kinds + diagnostic consequence text. |
|v0.1.38 |2026-05-27 |Clone-kind flow: collapsed three stages → two; post-commit jumps back to Manage kinds. |
|v0.1.37 |2026-05-27 |After confirmed delete-kind, re-open the palette at Manage kinds instead of closing. |
|v0.1.36 |2026-05-27 |Layer B: clone an existing kind to seed a new kind (Manage kinds → //+ Clone existing kind…//). |
|v0.1.35 |2026-05-27 |Delete-kind confirm dialog now shows live instance count. |
|v0.1.34 |2026-05-27 |Clone-from-existing in cascade creator flows (Layer A of the templating idea). |
|v0.1.33 |2026-05-27 |In-cascade //+ Create new <type>// rows in ref-field pickers — nested spawn flow with breadcrumb via the cascade stage stack. |
|v0.1.32 |2026-05-26 |Rename a field's key in the cascade. |
|v0.1.31 |2026-05-26 |Reorder kind fields via Ctrl-↑ / Ctrl-↓ in the cascade. |
|v0.1.30 |2026-05-26 |Live create-form preview while editing a kind in the cascade. |
|v0.1.29 |2026-05-26 |`k` leader: drill straight into Manage kinds. |
|v0.1.28 |2026-05-26 |Cross-link from instance → kind schema editor. |
|v0.1.27 |2026-05-26 |Fix: `:map[X]` silently drops every result past index 0; cross-kind option pool returned ~1 value instead of N. |
|v0.1.26 |2026-05-25 |Fix: enum options picker now also includes library common-field options + filters blanks. |
|v0.1.25 |2026-05-25 |Cross-kind option pool for enum picker. |
|v0.1.24 |2026-05-25 |Multi-pick sub-stage for enum options + shared array-append helper. |
|v0.1.23 |2026-05-25 |Fix: min/max constraint write was still buggy in 0.1.22 — subtract-of-existing didn't fire, validity filter let everything through. |
|v0.1.22 |2026-05-25 |Fix: setting min/max constraint via cascade prefixed all existing constraints, not just the new one. |
|v0.1.21 |2026-05-25 |Three new field-types with intrinsic format validation: `url` / `email` / `phone`. |
|v0.1.20 |2026-05-25 |Fix: nested JSON-array reads silently returned empty. |
|v0.1.19 |2026-05-25 |Parameterised constraints (`min:N` / `max:N` / custom) in the constraints picker. |
|v0.1.18 |2026-05-25 |Add / delete field syncs `kind.stream-fields`. |
|v0.1.17 |2026-05-25 |Validation hints on field rows. |
|v0.1.16 |2026-05-25 |//+ Add new field// defaults typed=text. |
|v0.1.15 |2026-05-25 |//+ Create new kind…// row in Manage-kinds. |
|v0.1.14 |2026-05-25 |Fix: //+ Add new field// was writing to a phantom tiddler. |
|v0.1.13 |2026-05-25 |DEL on a field row removes that field (uses cascade-palette 0.0.50's new `ca-on-delete`). |
|v0.1.12 |2026-05-25 |//+ Add new field// row in Manage-kinds. |
|v0.1.11 |2026-05-25 |Constraints / options / ref-types editing in the per-field stage. |
|v0.1.10 |2026-05-25 |//+ Add field from library//: common-fields picker in Manage-kinds. |
|v0.1.9 |2026-05-25 |Typed + cardinality as drill-pickers. |
|v0.1.8 |2026-05-25 |Per-field property editing. |
|v0.1.7 |2026-05-25 |Fix: Manage-kinds metadata rows showed //(unset)// everywhere + added per-kind field-list rows. |
|v0.1.6 |2026-05-25 |Fix: Manage-kinds entry showed nothing. |
|v0.1.5 |2026-05-25 |Cascade-palette: Manage kinds (edit existing type-defs). |
|v0.1.4 |2026-05-21 |Cascade-palette scope tiddler — `,<kind>` prefix restricts results to instances of that kind. |
|v0.1.3 |2026-05-21 |All three root entries carry `ca-group: Kind Actions` for shared header clustering. |
|v0.1.2 |2026-05-21 |Cascade integration — drill-fixing pass. |
|v0.1.1 |2026-05-21 |Cascade-palette integration: three root entries (//Find entity//, //Find by kind//, //Create entity//) + three universal actions (//Open//, //Edit fields//, //Delete//). |
|v0.1.0 |2026-05-20 |Initial release. One-tiddler-per-type schema with namespacing; hand-rolled editor/creator/view/stream-view/validator/type-builder; field types text/longtext/number/date/datetime/enum/ref + $title/$calculated; constraints required/min/max/unique/unique:wiki. |
